  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK251">
<l>taṉṉūṉ perukkaṟkut tāṉpiṟi tūṉuṇpā</l>
<l>ṉeṅṅaṉa māḷu maruḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>How can he be possessed of kindness, who to increase his own flesh, eats the flesh of other creatures.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
